text.data-name:
HOW TO MAKE IT Add ice to a copa glass and pour in 50 ml of Tanqueray London Dry. Add with 150 ml of fresh tonic water, add a wedge of lime to garnish and stir.
You will need: Tanqueray London Dry Gin, Tonic, lime, ice and Copa glass

text.data-name:
NEGRONI
HOW TO MAKE IT Build 35 ml Tanqueray London Dry Gin, 25 ml Italian aperitif bitters, 25 ml Sweet Vermouth, over ice and stir. Garnish with an orange twist.
You will need: Tanqueray London Dry Gin, Italian aperitif bitters, Sweet Vermouth, or
